textBeforeTable: Within the United States: Shipping Rates by Shipping Option and Location: We usually ship within 1-2 business days of receiving your order (sometimes sooner if possible!). All packages shipped within the United States will have delivery confirmation to ensure your package arrives safely. Gingersnaps Kids uses the US Postal Service's Priority Mail or Express Mail for shipping within the US.  We also ship internationally using USPS's Priority Mail International and Express Mail International. What Shipping Options Do You Offer? Gingersnaps Kids offers FREE* USPS Priority shipping on all orders over $100.00 to US shipping locations!
